  "prompt": "What is a good free spyware and antivirus?",
  "response": "There are several reliable free spyware and antivirus programs available. Here are a few recommendations:\n\n1. **Avast Free Antivirus**: Avast offers comprehensive protection against viruses, spyware, and other malware. It also includes features like a Wi-Fi scanner and a password manager.\n\n2. **AVG AntiVirus Free**: AVG provides robust protection against viruses, spyware, and other types of malware. It also includes features like email scanning and link protection.\n\n3. **Bitdefender Antivirus Free Edition**: Bitdefender offers solid protection with a minimalistic approach, focusing on the essentials to keep your system safe from viruses and spyware.\n\n4. **Microsoft Defender**: Included with Windows 10 and Windows 11, Microsoft Defender provides strong protection against viruses, spyware, and other malware. It's integrated into the operating system and regularly updated.\n\n5. **Malwarebytes Free**: While primarily known for its effectiveness in removing spyware and other malware, Malwarebytes can complement your existing antivirus software with its strong anti-malware capabilities.\n\n6. **Panda Free Antivirus**: Panda offers cloud-based antivirus protection, ensuring your system stays secure without consuming too many resources.\n\nEach of these programs has its strengths, so it's a good idea to evaluate them based on your specific needs and preferences.",
